SubString.CExoString: Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.
A portal glows softly before you. You wonder where it leads.
A small altar rests before you. You catch your reflection in its polished gleam, feeling somehow at peace within its presence. It seems as if it is asking for donations.
A heavy lever protrudes out of the ground, controlling some unseen mechanism below.
